        "## Augmentation Generators"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Bhqv6kNFHPL9"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# в”Җв”Җ Light augmentation (M1вҖ“M6) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n",
        "# Horizontal flip + small rotation only.\n",
        "# Vertical flip excluded вҖ” waste items have a natural upright orientation.\n",
        "datagen_light = ImageDataGenerator(\n",
        "    horizontal_flip=True,\n",
        "    rotation_range=15\n",
        ")\n",
        "datagen_light.fit(X_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "# в”Җв”Җ Strong augmentation (M7вҖ“M8) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n",
        "# Adds zoom and brightness jitter to expose the model to more variation.\n",
        "# Shear and vertical flip still excluded for semantic reasons.\n",
        "datagen_strong = ImageDataGenerator(\n",
        "    horizontal_flip=True,\n",
        "    rotation_range=20,\n",
        "    zoom_range=0.20,\n",
        "    brightness_range=[0.8, 1.2],\n",
        "    width_shift_range=0.10,\n",
        "    height_shift_range=0.10\n",
        ")\n",
        "datagen_strong.fit(X_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Augmentation generators ready.\")"
      ],
